title: [Swamp Carvings]
description: The bottom half of an old wine cask rests in the bed of this tiny cart, surrounded by some painted clay pots.  Each holds a collection of whimisically carved figures, nestled in cushioning sawdust.  Suspended by copper wires from the front of the cart is a carved wooden placard.
